# Movie Recommendation System - Frontend

## 🛠 Setup Instructions

### 1. Install Dependencies
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
```

### 2. Run Development Server
```bash
npm run dev
```

The frontend will run on **http://localhost:3000**

### 3. Build for Production
```bash
npm run build
```

## 🎨 Features Included

- **Netflix-style Dark UI** - Modern, clean design with Tailwind CSS
- **Authentication Pages** - Signup, Login, OTP verification
- **Movie Filter System** - Genre, Mood, Release Year, Rating
- **AI Recommendations** - Get personalized movie suggestions
- **Movie Grid Display** - Beautiful grid with posters and ratings
- **Responsive Design** - Works on mobile, tablet, desktop
- **Axios Integration** - API client with auto token injection
- **Framer Motion** - Smooth animations on hover
- **Favorites System** - Save movies to favorites

## 📋 Pages & Components

### Pages

**Auth.jsx** - Authentication page
- Signup form with name, email, password
- Login form
- OTP verification step
- Email resend functionality
- Form validation

**Home.jsx** - Main recommendation page
- Movie filter controls (genre, mood, year, rating)
- Get recommendations button
- Movie grid display
- Movie posters with ratings
- Add to favorites button
- Hover animations and details

### Components

**Navbar.jsx** - Top navigation
- Logo/branding
- Login/Logout buttons
- User menu (coming soon)

## 🚀 Technologies Used

- **React 18** - UI library
- **Vite** - Fast build tool & dev server
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework
- **Framer Motion** - Animation library
- **React Router v6** - Client-side routing
- **Axios** - HTTP client for API calls

## 🔗 API Integration

### Backend Connection
The frontend connects to backend running on `http://localhost:5000`

### API Endpoints Used

**Authentication** (`/api/auth`)
- `POST /signup` - Create new account
- `POST /verify-otp` - Verify email
- `POST /resend-otp` - Resend OTP
- `POST /login` - Login user

**Movies** (`/api/movies`)
- `GET /recommend` - Get AI recommendations with filters
- `GET /search` - Search movie by title
- `POST /favorite` - Add to favorites (requires token)
- `POST /wishlist` - Add to wishlist (requires token)
- `POST /history` - Add to watch history (requires token)
- `GET /profile` - Get user profile (requires token)

### Token Management

- Automatically saved to `localStorage` after login
- Automatically attached to protected API requests
- Automatically removed on logout

